== English ==
=== Phrase ===
'''[[God]] [[works]] [[in]] [[mysterious]] [[ways]]'''
# Expressing that a seemingly [[unfortunate]] or [[unfavourable]] situation or change may be [[beneficial]] later or [[in the long run]].
#: ''It seems that I'm about to be fired from my job. Well, '''God works in mysterious ways''' after all - maybe it'll be the kick I needed to on to [[University]]...''

==== Usage notes ====
As a [[figure of speech]], it does not usually denote the religion (or lack thereof) of the speaker.